com.shephertz.app42.iam
Interface App42InAppListener

public interface App42InAppListener

The listener interface for receiving app42InApp events. The class that is interested in processing a app42InApp event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addApp42InAppListener method. When the app42InApp event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.

Vishnu
